to that film.

04:01.006 --> 04:01.964
-[Janelle] Say that, Mama.
-[Earl] Wait.

04:02.094 --> 04:03.008
Y'all wanna know
the indisputable

04:03.139 --> 04:04.183
Black film, though?

04:04.270 --> 04:06.098
-What?
-What?

04:06.229 --> 04:07.926
