04:27.554 --> 04:29.469
Come on, now.

04:29.600 --> 04:30.688
Motherfuckin' Meteor Man.
Ain't nobody better.

04:30.819 --> 04:32.168
You can say what you want,
Earl,

04:32.255 --> 04:34.561
